  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "I was fortunate to find Kyle on a google search and after reading the reviews decided to contact him. I'm so glad I did. I had a challenging kitchen floor and hallway that needed leveling and lots more TLC.  Kyle was  not phased by the level of work that needed to be done and reassured me that he would be able to work with it. And he did! I am so pleased with my new floor. Kyle is professional and turned up as promised each day. His attention to detail is excellent  and his many years of experience show up in his work, going above and beyond to make sure the best job is done. Highly recommend him.",
      "reviewer": "Laura",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "I’ve had the pleasure to have Kyle work on both my kitchen and bathroom. Coming from the back of an awful experience where previous fitter/tiler went AWOL Kyle had to step in and I’m really glad he did. Reliable, punctual and very proud of his work- rightly so I’d add. I was kept up to date with progress and his expert advice came in handy with choosing the right tiles. I found his rates very fair as well. I would recommend him warmly to anyone and I look forward to working with him again. 10/10.",
      "reviewer": "Luca",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Kyle was brilliant - I found him through Google after our bathroom fitter said the tiles we wanted were a too complex for him.  Kyle did a brilliant job, was enthusiastic, turned up on time and got the job done in a good time (knowing we were on a strict deadline with a baby due the following week!) We'll definitely use him again in the future.",
      "reviewer": "Stephanie",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "10 / 10\nBest tradesmen I had the pleasure to work with and I would 100% recommend.\nExtreme attention to detail. Did not rush himself to finish the job and gave it plenty of time. Cleaned up after himself everyday. And went above and beyond the ask. Amazing tiling specially considering the floor was uneven!",
      "reviewer": "Paulo",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Kyle did some tiling work for us in our main bathroom. He is polite, professional and very hard working. Would definitely recommend him and use him again in the future. Thank you Kyle.",
      "reviewer": "Shel",
      "rating": 5
    }
  ],
